00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,375
 Paper prototyping involve drawing things simply on paper,

2
00:00:03,375 --> 00:00:05,730
 and it can be really good for experimenting with overall layouts,

3
00:00:05,730 --> 00:00:07,860
 especially because it tends to be a lot easier

